579
00:45:41,500 --> 00:45:44,625
are always bumptious people.

580
00:45:45,333 --> 00:45:50,500
So first of all station yourself within your Spirit,

581
00:45:50,750 --> 00:45:56,333
within your heart and try to develop your powers,

582
00:45:56,625 --> 00:45:59,542
inner powers, not of talking and showing off,

583
00:45:59,750 --> 00:46:02,792
but inner powers.

584
00:46:07,834 --> 00:46:11,709
Still so many are possessed, you know that.

585
00:46:11,999 --> 00:46:14,583
It's a shameful thing

586
00:46:14,792 --> 00:46:18,250
that even now in the temple of God there are people

587
00:46:18,542 --> 00:46:23,125
who are possessed by horrible evil things.

588
00:46:23,375 --> 00:46:26,125
How can it be?

589
00:46:26,500 --> 00:46:32,208
You are the carrier of all these, even now, how can it be?

590
00:46:36,458 --> 00:46:39,709
So one has to be very intensely there,

591
00:46:39,999 --> 00:46:42,375
and those today who are looking to be nothing,

592
00:46:42,583 --> 00:46:44,917
will grow into something so great,

593
00:46:45,083 --> 00:46:47,750
that you will be amazed at yourself.

594
00:46:47,999 --> 00:46:51,625
